title: Thai Basil Pork (Pad Ka-Prao Moo) | Kenji's Cooking Show
description:
A classic Thai street food. Super simple stir-fry that takes under 15 minutes start to finish.

Here's my friend Leela's original recipe: https://shesimmers.com/2012/05/pad-ka-prao-%E0%B8%9C%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%94%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%B0%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%9E%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B2.html
